name: notes2
description: Check your notes on every shared bot of the hub
long_description:
# Check your notes on every shared bot of the hub.

 .notes [bot|all] index
 .notes [bot|all] read  <#|all>
 .notes [bot|all] erase <#|all>

 may be numbers and/or intervals separated by ; ex: .notes erase 2-4;8;16-
     .notes noBOTy read all
